About Schmidt;;74;;85;;R;;Warren Schmidt (Jack Nicholson) has arrived at several of life's crossroads all at the same time. To begin with, he is retiring from a lifetime of service as an actuary for Woodmen of the World Insurance Company, and he feels utterly adrift. Furthermore, his only daughter Jeannie (Hope Davis) is about to marry a boob. And his wife Helen (June Squibb) dies suddenly after 42 years of marriage.;;Drama,Comedy;;Alexander Payne;;2002;;Jack Nicholson,Hope Davis,Dermot Mulroney,Kathy Bates,Len Cariou,Howard Hesseman,June Squibb,Harry Groener;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/about_schmidt